- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper proposes a novel approach to solve optimization problems using evolutionary algorithms and machine learning techniques. 
- cs.DM (Data Mining) is a possible category as the paper uses a training data set to train a classifier and filter candidate solutions. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper proposes a new strategy to improve the performance of evolutionary algorithms, which can be relevant to software engineering applications.
